Name: Ration Bar
Desc: Increases the DEF of all Resonators in the team by 36% for 15 minutes. In Co-op games, it only affects your own Resonators.
Bg: Calcharo has a fondness for Huanglong's Food Ration Bar. He believes it efficiently satisfies basic energy needs in the wild and has a unique taste. To cater to some of the younger merc's preferences, Calcharo has enhanced the bar by adding dried fruits, sugar beans, and various seasonings, creating a variety of flavors.
